We therefore ask the Government to urge TFL to:
•	Prioritise the Chesham branch over the Amersham branch (the latter is serviced by the Chiltern line as well as the Met line);
•	Prioritise maintenance of rolling stock and the branch line to minimise technical failure;
•	Prioritise consistency of service before 9am and after 4pm; 
•	Provide accurate and timely information to passengers so that they may plan around any disruption and avoid being stranded far from home.
